**Example 1: 获取黑洞解封次数**



Input: 

```
tccli dayu DescribeUnBlockStatis --cli-unfold-argument ```

```
{
    "Response": {
        "BeginTime": "2018-09-10 00:00:00",
        "EndTime": "2018-09-11 00:00:00",
        "RequestId": "20fe3e59-03ab-4418-86d6-242851af62e4",
        "Total": 3,
        "Used": 0
    }
}
```
